title: PlaiFm
text: Hello and welcome to PlaiFM! We are a unique internet radio station. We are currently based in the UK. We are currently unable to host radio shows due to the fact we have not got our licence yet (we're working on it!). PlaiFM was founded by Rhys, Jenson, and Matt on the 22/10/22. Since then we have been working nonstop to produce a wonderful station.
